en_982198_0	Troops of the 58 Division contribute their valuable time to impart knowledge on basic weapon handling technologies to school Cadets in the Devapathiraja National School, Galle as another community project.
en_982198_1	The training was given on Wednesday (10) at Sri Lanka Light Infantry Training School, Boossa.
en_982198_2	It is customary for Cadets to undergo their Cadet training at various District Secretariats around the island.
en_982198_3	This basic training was given on the directions of the Major General Sudath Perera, General Officer Commanding, 58 Division.
